Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再 再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再跟我比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经输得差不多了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了最终的胜利…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时的失败根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像有点明白艾尔奇亚被逼到如此地步的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定是完美无缺的运气比试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的鸟几秒之后会飞走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧让你先猜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向盟约宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(424,437)}Assent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几秒后？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向盟约宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(424,437)}Assent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就3秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…你这是犯规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又没有设定那种规则 没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我就是赢不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了艾尔奇亚 为了「人类种」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:17:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连一次偶然我也无法抓住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世上根本没有所谓的运气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规则 前提 心理状态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由无数不可见的变数所导致的无法预测的必然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让游戏的胜败在开始之前就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不会有偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一副除去鬼牌的扑克里 抽到黑桃A的概率是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(288,437)\fs21}Joker
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是52分之1吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果是全新的扑克呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新扑克牌的顺序在某种程度上是固定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除去鬼牌最下面那张几乎百分百是黑桃A
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(247,437)\fs21}Joker
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我从来没说过这是一副新的扑克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是 不知道而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道 可能性就会从1.92%变为100%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结论就是 知道的人必然会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你和「人类种」不断惨败的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(395,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我们「卡关」的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 卡关…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报不足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说想进攻兽耳王国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却完全找不到「兽人种」的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(483,437)\fs21}Warbeast
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的仅仅是他们第六感很敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看穿他人想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的话 那虚张声势和策略都不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本无法与其进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们查阅了王宫里所有的书本资料仍一无所获
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果城镇里连一间图书馆或书店都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家还想不想混下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你们即位之后一直在收集这个世界的情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无胜算却一味进攻 白痴才做得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不采取行动只会停滞不前而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了艾尔奇亚就算献上这幅身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想及早尽一份力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步走错 满盘皆输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家…「人类种」已经被逼至如此境地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人并没有玩忽职守
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩负着「人类种」三百万人的性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却连这点都没发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙好像也在为这个国家贡献着自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我们的改革 反抗的人出乎意料的少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你从中调解了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙 真能干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空 白…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来也请多指教 史蒂芙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.96,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,汪汪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此「卡关」依然不变…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的突破口也缺少关键的「钥匙」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 天突然黑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壮观…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉普达真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}注：出自著名动画电影《天空之城》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是「阿邦特·赫伊姆」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「幻想种」之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(393,437)\fs21}Fantasma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位阶序列第二位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(245,298)\3c&H934BC1&\bord2\shad0\fs28\be5}「幻想种」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(245,270)\3c&H934BC1&\bord2\shad0\fs20\be5}Fantasma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(332,347)\3c&H934BC1&\bord2\shad0\fs28\be5}[十六种族]位阶序列第二位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(244,319)\3c&H934BC1&\bord2\shad0\fs20\be5}Exceed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样才能跟那种东西玩游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 就在那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将「天空都市」上的「天翼种」拉拢为同伴才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们要怎样去那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴[哔~]斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}注：neta毁灭拉普达的咒语「巴鲁斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不掉下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界的服务器真坚挺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天翼种」的话附近就有一位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(285,437)\fs21}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…约五年前出现在「国立艾尔奇亚大图书馆」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爷爷进行游戏将整个图书馆以及所有藏书赢走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 原来这里有图书馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将知识搬上赌桌 你爷爷是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是人类唯一的武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人看着啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十六种族位阶序列第六位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(317,437)\fs21}Exceed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天翼种」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在远古大战中 为弑神而创造出来的尖兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到原来在这么近的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空 真的要挑战那种预料之外的怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位弑神者所拥有的关于这个世界的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是我们唯一的突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想来可以不来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙 按照传统「天翼种」玩的游戏只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(412,437)\fs21}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 文献是这么写的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就从这里开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称霸世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:22:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 天使大人究竟在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不是优雅的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就是「死亡」本身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse 那边的Person们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到Me的Library有What事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气氛全没了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么死了真是何等失态
